            <p><a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/baldurs-gate-3-a-critical-success-with-critical-failures">Baldur's Gate 3</a> may soon be an Xbox Play Anywhere title, according to a presumed premature advert spotted on the Xbox Store.</p>
<p>I don't personally see the advert on the Xbox store, either on console or PC, but <a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/xbox/comments/1ohg4ay/baldurs_gate_3_xbox_play_anywhere/">an image was captured on Reddit</a> showing a Baldur's Gate 3 promo block with the words "Now Xbox Play Anywhere" on it. This could have been faked but the scruffy nature of it and the odd angle make it a convincing fake if so.</p>
<p>I asked Larian for clarification this morning but its position is "no comment" for now, which I think bodes well.</p>

